Beginner friendly shy girl workout ☺️💗

If you are new to the gym and are not comfortable with using the machines yet try this workout!

Jacks w/ press
Marching 
Bare crawl into push up
3 rounds x 45sec each 

Squat w/ press
Alternating forward lunges w/ press
Alternating side lunges w/ press
3 rounds x 45sec each 

Russian twist
Leg raises holding weight overhead 
Toe reaches w/ weight
3 rounds x 45sec each

Skin care routine with a little eyebrows lol

I’m a girl that loves makeup and I love to wear it everyday but on the days when it’s 96 degrees outside I can’t do my daily beat lol it will literally melt off my face.. Yes, I workout in makeup No it doesn’t bother my skin at all and I’ve been doing it for 3 years now

I need to find something to help with my dark marks if you have any recommendations please let me know!

I use..
African black soap 
CeraVe daily moisturizer @cerave 
Black girl sunscreen @blackgirlsunscreen 
Lashes @taylominks
Eyebrow gel @elfcosmetics 
Eyebrow pencil is from the hair store lol
And if you are not using it as a lip liner you should try!

I’m very happy and blessed to be growing this beautiful baby inside me 💗 I’m finally entering motherhood 😂

These past 4 months have been so stressful and draining with the non stop sickness. Let’s not get me started on how everything about my body is changing every week. 

Fitness has been my love and passion for some years and this past year I have really lost it but now is the time to fight through and get back to it… I know a lot of people watch me and get inspired so I will document my next 5 months in the gym ☺️ Dm me if you have any questions!
